title: LWS: Robert Fico resigns, Slovakia has a new ruling cabinet
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary:
Robert Fico resigns, Peter Pellegrini to replace him as prime minister. 
International team will join the investigation of the murder of investigative journalist Jan Kuciak and his fiancee Martina Kusnirova. 
Bratislava’s Alien Police department has moved. 

This programme is part of The Slovak Spectator subscription and our readers are receiving it every Thursday morning as part of their subscription.
